cross: Paphiopedilum President Fred x Paphiopedilum Magically Wood

measurements.description: One symmetrical flower on one 23.2-cm inflorescence; arising from a 3-growth 21.5-cm plant; sepals white overlaid green centrally, rose suffused marginally, venation green; petals white, basally green, distally rose, veining cordovan, random deep mahogany raised spots, superior margins hirsute; pouch maroon, veining darker maroon; staminode light green, dark green centrally; substance firm; texture glossy.
